com.esri.mo2.data.feat
Interface Data

All Known Subinterfaces:
Element, Element, Feature, GroupElement, Identifiable, Image, MapData, Row, ServerImage, Spatial, Tile
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseElement, BaseElement, BaseFeature, BaseGroupElement, BaseRow, BaseServerImage, DbaseRow
public interface Data

A Data is one unit of information that can be obtained from a Dataset. The search method of a Dataset, returns a Cursor identifying those Data objects that satisfy the search criteria.

See Also:
Dataset, Cursor
